---
title: Mexican Chicken Wraps with Appley Beetroot Slaw and Potato Wedges
description: Well, hello Mr. Beetroot! You’re looking awfully delicious! We’re making the best of wonderful seasonal vegetables in our Mexican chicken wraps with appley beetroot slaw and potato wedges.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-chicken-wraps-wk2-7c37b87b.jpg
